{"tid":612263,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［少圖 冇字］ 日本遊記","createTime":"2018-03-31T17:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T03:22:47.000Z","uid":133050,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8cac31e50032d77ec55b48431c6fcdb797b1f0","tid":612263,"uid":133050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"行程： 大阪- 京都-東京-奈良-大阪<br />\n<br />\n第一次寫遊記 帶定頭盔先 有咩寫得唔好 唔好怪我 我盡量多圖小字啦 因為我文筆係有d 差 可能會寫到1999 同可能會不定時update <br />\n<br />\n成個行程12日其實都有啲趕 除左食下嘢買下嘢都冇咩行咩景點 溫泉原本想去但都冇時間 <br />\n<br />\n咁多日比較難忘都係食左餐 Kobe beef 懷石料理同約左個識左好耐嘅架妹fd 出黎食飯<br />\n<br />\n機場啲例牌相 我就唔影啦直接影下啲嘢食啦<br />\n<br />\n第一日落機 已經係夜晚八點幾 即刻去醫肚先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/011533_5dc0bd853c4de4ef9e82abac4e63be81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F011533_5dc0bd853c4de4ef9e82abac4e63be81.png&h=2b9b1425&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/011537_a7b3bbd94af0f2708234d973757abcbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F011537_a7b3bbd94af0f2708234d973757abcbe.png&h=45a5b070&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1415d4f6eecd5f8b8275dc78fd76877f2ba66120","tid":612263,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:19:46.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeee1e0a9769e65e78c71e27bb4db0c347b591fa","tid":612263,"uid":176873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37789993c96fc593b43a08a2352a8cad08cbaeb","tid":612263,"uid":33330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"lm睇架妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"