food 食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日係我地最後一日lunch Time係大阪 所以我哋就去咗食Kobe beef  佢哋lunch同dinner 嗰個價錢可以去到差一倍到兩倍  晏晝分量會細少少 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/104901_d8f40949064f9f80d4b6f962fe8dd603.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F104901_d8f40949064f9f80d4b6f962fe8dd603.png&h=62edb1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/104819_8cead95ad82e360f31b19d62745d824c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F104819_8cead95ad82e360f31b19d62745d824c.png&h=b4491969&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a454397ec4470c0a82c93f80624e6783320b9ba1","tid":612263,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"518f49bceb4d154180f53d9ff3fc64fe67ec3738","tid":612263,"uid":133050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee729c1643512f15d8da5261c34c4c2b27ea9f64","tid":612263,"uid":140481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T10:53:43.000Z","msg":"預咗幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"前前後後唔計機票 兩條友應該洗左兩萬左右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"差不多啦"},{"pid":"9e0d9476e611eed174065a58884b4973a2a14cc9","tid":612263,"uid":177831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T23:30:42.000Z","msg":"唔去黑門市場可以去邊個市場?"},{"pid":"c392b46b7d12d33c923b44a3c1736d0e32325f70","tid":612263,"uid":133050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0d9476e611eed174065a58884b4973a2a14cc9","tid":612263,"uid":177831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T23:30:42.000Z","msg":"唔去黑門市場可以去邊個市場?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:22:47.000Z","msg":"叫天滿市場 我日頭冇去過  淨係夜晚試過食飯 所以賣